Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.16,0:52:09.70,English,,0,0,0,,Which you can think of a process as a running program
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.16,0:52:09.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在这里我们可以把进程想成一个正在运行的程序
